Attributes.Name: Direct Children Count
Attributes.Note: Indicates the direct children count for a Hierarchical Requirement

Attributes.Name: Blocked Reason
Attributes.Note: The reason this artifact is blocked

Attributes.Name: HasParent
Attributes.Note: Indicates whether this Hierarchical Requirement has a parent

Attributes.Name: In Progress Date
Attributes.Note: The date this hierarchical requirement went in-progress.

Attributes.Name: Recycled
Attributes.Note: Moved to Recycle Bin

Attributes.Name: Defect Status
Attributes.Note: The status of the Defects associated with this artifact.

Attributes.Name: Task Status
Attributes.Note: The status of the Tasks associated with this artifact.

Attributes.Name: Defects
Attributes.Note: The Defects associated with this artifact.

Attributes.Name: Blocker
Attributes.Note: The blocker blocking this artifact.

Attributes.Name: Task Remaining Total
Attributes.Note: Task remaining total of this artifact

Attributes.Name: Task Actual Total
Attributes.Note: Task actual total of this artifact

Attributes.Name: Task Estimate Total
Attributes.Note: Task estimate total of this artifact

Attributes.Name: Blocked
Attributes.Note: Flag to determine if this artifact is blocked

Attributes.Name: Plan Estimate
Attributes.Note: Plan estimate of this artifact

Attributes.Name: Rank
Attributes.Note: Schedule rank

Attributes.Name: Schedule State
Attributes.Note: Schedule state

Attributes.Name: Iteration
Attributes.Note: The iteration that this artifact is scheduled in

Attributes.Name: Tasks
Attributes.Note: Tasks associated with completing.

Attributes.Name: Accepted Date
Attributes.Note: The date that this artifact's schedule state was set to accepted.  This is automatically set.

Attributes.Name: Children
Attributes.Note: The children of the requirement (read-only collection)

Attributes.Name: Parent
Attributes.Note: The parent of the requirement.

Attributes.Name: Workspace
Attributes.Note: A reference to the workspace an object is associated with.  This field can only be set during object creation.

Attributes.Name: Subscription
Attributes.Note: A read-only reference to the subscription an object is associated with.

Attributes.Name: Package
Attributes.Note: The package that this requirement is assigned to.

Attributes.Name: Attachments
Attributes.Note: Attachments associated with this requirement

Attributes.Name: Ready
Attributes.Note: Whether or not this Artifact is ready

Attributes.Name: Changesets
Attributes.Note: Changesets associated with this artifact.

Attributes.Name: Owner
Attributes.Note: Artifact owner, a reference to the user.

Attributes.Name: Tags
Attributes.Note: Tags for Artifact

Attributes.Name: Discussion
Attributes.Note: The discussions for this artifact.

Attributes.Name: Last Update Date
Attributes.Note: The last update date of an object.  It is automatically assigned when an object is created or updated.

Attributes.Name: Project
Attributes.Note: The project this artifact is associated with.

Attributes.Name: Revision History
Attributes.Note: A reference to the revision history (read-only) of the artifact.

Attributes.Name: Description
Attributes.Note: Artifact description, which is a rich-text field.

Attributes.Name: Name
Attributes.Note: The name of the artifact

Attributes.Name: Formatted ID
Attributes.Note: The formatted ID for an object.  This is automatically assigned when an object is created and can never be changed.  In queries, only include the integer portion and omit the prefix.

Attributes.Name: Creation Date
Attributes.Note: The creation date of an object.  It is automatically assigned when an object is created, and can never be changed.

Attributes.Name: Object ID
Attributes.Note: This is the object ID, a globally-unique identifier for the object.  It is automatically assigned when an object is created, and can never be changed.
